            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with a matching lid) with 1 tbsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp] </span>[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>harissa meat-free mince mix</strong> and cook for 3-4 min or until beginning to brown all over, breaking it up with a wooden spoon as you go</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
