      "instruction": "<p>Once cooked, transfer the<strong> harissa meat-free mince</strong> to a clean mixing bowl, reserve the pan</p><p>Add your <strong>soy sauce</strong> and 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong> and mix to combine</p>",
